---
By: Marcus Aurelius
Locus:
  Page: 163
  Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Fault
---
>3 * Fault-finding Regarding that which happens in harmony with nature, we
ought to blame neither gods, for they do nothing wrong either voluntarily
or involuntarily, nor men, for they do nothing wrong except unconsciously.
Consequently, we shall blame no one.
